xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 27, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104biz1719502191613.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/biz1719502191613.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/biz1719502191613.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ask1665702602873\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $instancevalidation\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ask1665702602873___instancevalidation_270407\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Identify whether data in the component instance requires validation.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ask1665702602873__topic_d84824e1_d84825e1_d84826e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ask1665702602873__p_d84827e1_d84828e1_d84829e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancevalidation</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ask1665702602873__topic_d56237e1_d56238e1_d56239e1_d56240e1_d56241e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d711123e75\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ask1665702602873__d6052e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ask1665702602873__d6052e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ask1665702602873__d6052e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ask1665702602873__d6052e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__d6052e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__d6052e20__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__d6052e20__entry__3\">Name of component instance; optional. If\n\t\t\t\t omitted, the current instance is used. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ask1665702602873__topic_d56242e1_d56243e1_d56244e1_d56245e1_d56246e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d711123e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8861e1_d8862e1_d8863e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancevalidation</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8861e1_d8862e1_d8863e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8861e1_d8862e1_d8863e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8861e1_d8862e1_d8863e1__entry__1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8861e1_d8862e1_d8863e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8861e1_d8862e1_d8863e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8861e1_d8862e1_d8863e1__entry__2\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ask1665702602873__li_d34589e1_d34590e1_d34591e1\">No data has been modified.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ask1665702602873__li_d34592e1_d34593e1_d34594e1\">All the data has already been successfully validated.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\">You can check the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancemod</span> to determine which of these situations applies.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8861e1_d8862e1_d8863e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8861e1_d8862e1_d8863e1__entry__2\">\n Data requires validation.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following this\n            Function</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__2\"> Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__3\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-57 </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__3\"> The named instance cannot be found in the\n\t\t\t\t component pool. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1101 </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_FIELD&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__3\"> An incorrect field name was provided;\n\t\t\t\t either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component.\n\t\t\t\t </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1105 </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_INSTANCE&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__3\"> The instance name provided is not valid.\n\t\t\t\t For example, the argument contains incorrect characters. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ryt1665702577808.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryt1665702577808.html\" title=\"Creates a new instance of a component.\">newinstance</a>.\n                             </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1304 </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_UNKNOWN_CONTEXT&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ask1665702602873__table_d8864e1_d8865e1_d8866e1__entry__3\"> Function not allowed, unknown context.\n\t\t\t\t The <var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var> argument was omitted and one of the following occurred: <p class=\"p\">There is no current instance, for\n\t\t\t\t example, in the apStart trigger.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The current instance is a form started\n\t\t\t\t with <code class=\"ph codeph\">run</code>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ask1665702602873__topic_d56247e1_d56248e1_d56249e1_d56250e1_d56251e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d711123e362\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ask1665702602873__d6417e20\">Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ask1665702602873__topic_d56252e1_d56253e1_d56254e1_d56255e1_d56256e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d711123e372\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ask1665702602873__p_d84845e1_d84846e1_d84847e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancevalidation</span> checks if any occurrence in the current component instance requires validation. This can be viewed as an inclusive OR of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span> for all occurrences in the instance.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ask1665702602873__section_l1w_y5k_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d711123e387\">Example: Checking the Validation Status of a Form </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancevalidation</span> to\n            check the validation status of the current form:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ask1665702602873__pre_mt2_z5k_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">if ($instancevalidation = 1)\n message/info \"Some data has not been validated.\"\nendif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702576500.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Validate</a><p>Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qdc1665702602510.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a field requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/atw1665702600492.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancemod</a><p>Return or set the modification status of data in the current component instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcw1719485700746.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpz1719812992669.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occvalidation</a><p>Check whether an occurrence requires validation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419703\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419703\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$instancevalidation Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $instancevalidation Identify whether data in the component instance requires validation. $instancevalidation { ( InstanceName ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description InstanceName String Name of component instance; optional. If omitted, the current instance is used. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $instancevalidation Value Meaning \"\" An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. 0 No data has been modified. All the data has already been successfully validated. You can check the value of $instancemod to determine which of these situations applies. 1 Data requires validation. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following this Function Value Error constant Meaning -57 <UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE> The named instance cannot be found in the component pool. -1101 <UPROCERR_FIELD> An incorrect field name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component. -1105 <UPROCERR_INSTANCE> The instance name provided is not valid. For example, the argument contains incorrect characters. For more information, see newinstance . -1304 <UPROCERR_UNKNOWN_CONTEXT> Function not allowed, unknown context. The InstanceName argument was omitted and one of the following occurred: There is no current instance, for example, in the apStart trigger. The current instance is a form started with run . Use Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports. Description The function $instancevalidation checks if any occurrence in the current component instance requires validation. This can be viewed as an inclusive OR of $occvalidation for all occurrences in the instance. Example: Checking the Validation Status of a Form The following example uses $instancevalidation to check the validation status of the current form: if ($instancevalidation = 1) message/info \"Some data has not been validated.\" endif Copy Related Links Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). $fieldvalidation Identify whether a field requires validation. $instancemod Return or set the modification status of data in the current component instance. $keyvalidation Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation. $occvalidation Check whether an occurrence requires validation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}